|==========| POCO F1 / Beryllium |==========|

Komodo OS v4.3 | Official
Codename: SweetPea
Build date: 20/06/2022
by @zkyzzz

Source Changelog:
• Merged June 2022 patch
• Bump version to 4.3 Codename SweetPea
• Merged android-12.1.0_r8
• Full Changelog: (https://komodo-os.my.id/changelog.html)

Device Changelogs:
• Adapt new statusbar dimens
• Fixed PowerOffAlarm
• Fixed unable to add Emergency contact
• Disable slow blur effect
• Enable usage of dex2oat64
• Update Surfaceflinger props
• Update config_wallpaperMaxScale value
• Added one-handed mode
• Several SELinux denial fixes
• Synced with latest Silvercore kernel changes

Notes:
• Toxicofera & GApps build
• System_Ext Support Not Added
• You Can Flash Any Non-System_ext Supported Kernel

Thanks To:
• Allah SWT
• Komodo OS Team
• #xisan & #XtremeOrnob for base trees
• #Excraze & #HeshamGazzaz for help and fixes
• #Reignz3 for kernel
• All testers

